N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 69.6 - Actions after service of petition

State Regulations

The petitioner and the Commissioner of Labor may file with
the board such further relevant matter in writing as they think proper, provided that the board's proceedings shall not be delayed
thereby. Notes
